<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="plate-n">plate <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pleɪt/    美 /pleɪt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>盘子；碟子；一道菜：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a plate of fish 
一盘鱼</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a cold plate 
一道凉菜</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>板块；(金属等的) 平板：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the Pacific plate
太平洋板块</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The ship is covered with <strong>steel plates</strong>. 
这船的外壳包裹着钢板。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>(印有名字或数字的) 金属牌：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a car’s <strong>license plate</strong> 
汽车牌照</p></div></div>